The collection is composed of over 200 visual traits and 100 audio traits. Each NFT will be an MP4 file with an accompanying GIF as the cover image. We created our own in-house code to apply an audio layer to your NFT, unlocking a new meta for you to experience.

 

FishBallerz are an experiment created by Capt'n Glubber. After losing his father during a fishing trip while he was young, Glubber swore revenge on all fish in the sea. Day in, day out, Capt'n Glubber can be found sweeping the seas or experimenting on Fish, granting them consciousness to do his bidding.

FishBallerz Glub Members grant holder-only benefits and exclusive access to Sloppy Studios.
